<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>LedgerMind - AI Bookkeeper</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial; max-width: 800px; margin: 50px auto; padding: 20px; background: #0f172a; color: white; text-align: center; }
        h1 { color: #38bdf8; font-size: 40px; }
        .btn { background: #38bdf8; padding: 15px 30px; color: black; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; }
        .feature { background: #1e293b; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 8px; text-align: left; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>LedgerMind AI Bookkeeper</h1>
    <p>Upload your QuickBooks/CSV and get instant AI insights</p>
    
    <div class="feature">✅ Find duplicate transactions automatically</div>
    <div class="feature">✅ Detect potential tax deductions over $500</div>
    <div class="feature">✅ Flag suspicious/fraud activity</div>
    
    <h3>API Endpoint: /scan</h3>
